Transmitter (ESP32 + MPU6500)

MPU6500 VCC  → ESP32 3.3V
MPU6500 GND  → ESP32 GND
MPU6500 SDA  → ESP32 GPIO 21
MPU6500 SCL  → ESP32 GPIO 22
MPU6500 AD0  → GND
-- ESP32 powered via USB or LiPo (5V to VIN)

Receiver (ESP32 + L298N + 4 Motors)
ESP32 → L298N (Control Pins)

IN1 → GPIO 23
IN2 → GPIO 22
IN3 → GPIO 19
IN4 → GPIO 18
ENA → GPIO 25
ENB → GPIO 26
